In a #bowl{}, combine the @heavy cream{1%cup} and @buttermilk{2%Tbsp}. Cover with a #clean kitchen cloth{} in a warm, draft-free place and let sit until thickened, but still a pourable consistency, 12 to ~{16%hours}. Stir and refrigerate until ready to use. (Can be refrigerated for up to 1 week.)
